inuum limit extrapolations and produces remarkably\nprecise results, thus showing the feasibility of these techniques for gauge\ntheory problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Oct 2013 17:01:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-04"}
