llow the edges of the old channels. For larger {\\Delta}t (10-200 {\\mu}s)\nthe new streamers start to increase in size and move to the centre of the old\nchannel. Finally, around millisecond timescales the new channels are completely\nindependent of the old channels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Oct 2013 09:49:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Nov 2013 13:28:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-24"}
